Classic TT Highlights 2016 (ITV)

Arts Documentary hosted by Steve Parrish and James Whitham and Steve Plater, published by ITV in 2016 - English narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/3/30/Classic-TT-Highlights-2016-ITV-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
Steve Parrish, James Whitham and Steve Plater are in the thick of all the excitement at this year's Isle of Man Classic TT. A real festival for all motorbike fans with a stunning mix of vintage and modern machines on show, and in action. TT stars of the past and present including John McGuinness, Michael Dunlop and Bruce Anstey. They race around the legendary Mountain Course, and join in the fun of the Paddock Carnival, parade laps, chat shows, autograph sessions and the TT Heroes dinner.
